node.text: These two are off to new adventures, so we have to wave farewell. My heart is breaking 💔. Good luck, it was great seeing you @wildhairdresser.au #seeyouinacoupleofyears #missyoualready #siblings #roadtripping #westernaustralia #gypsylife
Travel Update: massive power outage today, including dinner in the dark #westernaustralia #whataday #cervantes #wetravelinthedark

We did it 🥳
Shout out to my kick-ass sister, who went from “whom the hell are we running from?” to marathon finisher in 4 months. I made her run intervalls and tempo-runs, which she hated, but she made it through all of them, while cursing all the way. Nonetheless, she proofed herself being a very good long distance runner. I’m so happy, I have been part of the process
